The battlefields are located in ~powerman directory 
One forest near Helgrath is located in ~detach/forbiden directory 
Some weapons and armour in play are located in ~detach/azeria/obj directory
Darkmouth caverns in Roston is located in ~detach/darkmouth directory
 
All these things need a header file done sometime and their own directory added
to /d
 
