aciri, citrin.old, house(??), lca, nemar, quests.bak, radyne, shadow.bak,
tombar, vswamp(??)

You can't change anything in the metaisland directory because root was given to ftp. If there is a problem or bug in metaisland area, post it on stormbringer's board so he can fix it through ftp.
